Launching Esco - Your Excel AI Agent

Feeling stuck with the same old tasks on Excel or CSV files? Ever tried making a VBA macro and got lost because it was too tricky?

Esco is here to help

Esco is the first-ever AI agent that helps you automate those repeat Excel/CSV tasks without any excel formulas as Esco understands English.

Here's what you can do with Esco: * Upload Excel sheets or CSVs and analyse them in English. * Do complex things like regression analysis and predictions without needing to code. * Save your steps/workflow and do them again with just one click in future.

Esco is something special we've built using our own LLMops infrastructure. DM me if you are looking to create Esco like agents in your organisation.
